      <title>印度与欧盟展开谈判，监管期限十月临近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/india-eu-in-negotiations-as-october-deadline-on-oversight-looms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度和欧洲监管机构正在展开激烈讨论，以解决当地清算所的监管问题，并要求银行在 10 月底截止日期前做出替代安排。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/india-eu-in-negotiations-as-october-deadline-on-oversight-looms</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 09:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将对中国电动汽车征收最高 45% 关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-votes-to-impose-tariffs-of-up-to-45-on-china-made-evs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，欧盟周五投票决定对来自中国的电动汽车征收高达 45% 的关税，此举将加剧与北京的贸易紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/eu-votes-to-impose-tariffs-of-up-to-45-on-china-made-evs</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 09:00:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国就业报告公布后，交易员准备迎接标普 500 指数的进一步波动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/traders-gird-for-more-s-p-500-volatility-after-us-jobs-report</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五美国非农就业报告将出炉，交易员们准备迎接额外的波动，市场将密切关注该报告，寻找美联储 11 月份将降息多少的信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/traders-gird-for-more-s-p-500-volatility-after-us-jobs-report</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 09:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行计划转移与 20 亿欧元企业贷款相关的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/hsbc-plans-risk-transfer-linked-to-2-billion-of-corporate-loans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，汇丰控股有限公司计划发行一笔与约 20 亿欧元（22 亿美元）企业贷款组合相关的重大风险转移债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/hsbc-plans-risk-transfer-linked-to-2-billion-of-corporate-loans</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 08:58:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国银行预计印度外汇储备将在 2026 年 3 月达到 7450 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/bofa-sees-india-s-forex-pile-reaching-745-billion-in-march-2026</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国银行表示，到 2026 年 3 月，印度的外汇储备可能会增至 7450 亿美元，这将为印度央行提供更多影响卢比的潜在力量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/bofa-sees-india-s-forex-pile-reaching-745-billion-in-march-2026</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 08:54:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
