    <item>
      <title>股市上涨刺激需求，人人都想购买港元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/hong-kong-dollar-in-rare-spotlight-as-stock-rally-boosts-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着在香港交易所上市的中国股票大幅上涨，需求飙升，长期处于休眠状态的香港货币开始苏醒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/hong-kong-dollar-in-rare-spotlight-as-stock-rally-boosts-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 03:24:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国股市交易员思考股市大涨能走多远</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/chinese-stocks-in-hong-kong-climb-as-traders-assess-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着香港中国股市完成自 2007 年以来最佳两周涨势，人们开始质疑这轮反弹能持续多久。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-04/chinese-stocks-in-hong-kong-climb-as-traders-assess-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Oct 2024 02:12:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价上涨，美国就业数据公布前股市举步维艰：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国关键就业数据公布之前，欧洲股市和美国股指期货艰难上涨，这些数据可能明确利率走势。随着交易员追踪中东敌对行动的升级，油价延续涨势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 22:27:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中东风险推动油价创两年来最大周涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-4</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于担心以色列可能决定袭击伊朗石油设施以报复其领土遭受导弹袭击，油价有望创下两年来最大单周涨幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-4</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 22:12:22 GMT</pubDate>
